snippet.title: Bibb deputies investigating after inmate stabbed at the jail
snippet.description:
The Bibb County Sheriff’s Office is investigating a stabbing at the jail. They say Arlandus Fort is in stable condition after being stabbed twice in his cell block.
By email, the sheriff’s office says Fort was stabbed with a “sharp object,” but they’re still investigating details.
